        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/tehabe/{size}/9333_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-09-13T20:50:22.298Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I noticed that in iOS 26, Apple finally noticed that putting things on the bottom of the screen of a smartphone is a good idea. In Messages and even in Mail the buttons for creating a new message on the bottom of the screen. Something which Android made with the FAB years ago, I know.</p>\n<p>I hope Signal will follow this new UI guideline in a coming update, like it shows here in Messages:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/9/2/92ce1bed61eb95fee8ac3fc9c6825d973083389d.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/92ce1bed61eb95fee8ac3fc9c6825d973083389d\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-13 at 22.49.03\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/2/92ce1bed61eb95fee8ac3fc9c6825d973083389d_2_345x86.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-13 at 22.49.03\" data-base62-sha1=\"kWHir75QiSPUfAP3MaRGurgj1NP\" width=\"345\" height=\"86\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/2/92ce1bed61eb95fee8ac3fc9c6825d973083389d_2_345x86.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/2/92ce1bed61eb95fee8ac3fc9c6825d973083389d_2_517x129.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/2/92ce1bed61eb95fee8ac3fc9c6825d973083389d_2_690x172.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"0E0E0E\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-13 at 22.49.03</span><span class=\"informations\">1170×293 14.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
