        "created_at": "2025-09-14T06:48:09.921Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I’m not exactly sure how this should be done. In messages it’s easy as there’s no tabs. In the App Store they put search as the last tab. Neither of these methods seem like a good idea for Signal, so I’m not sure.</p>",
